--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The following is a list of the major customizations made to the lua-5.1.4
sources for BZFlag. Many of the source code changes can be found by searching
for the 'BZ' tag, ex:  'cd src/; grep BZ *.cxx *.h'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Renamed Makefile to Makefile.orig, and  (svn r18913)
   src/Makefile to src/Makefile.org

2. Added Makefile.am  (svn r18913)

3. Renamed the source files from .c to .cxx for g++ compilation  (svn r19274)

4. Fixed a casting problem in loadlib.cxx/ll_sym()

5. Added the __usedindex metamethod  (svn r19401)

6. Added the __rawset metamethod and luaL_checkrawset() funciton  (svn r19402)

7. Added the luaL_testudata() function  (rumoured to be in lua 5.2)

8. Fixed a g++ HUGE_VAL issue at the top of lmathlib.cxx

9. Appended '(BZFlag)' to the LUA_VERSION and LUA_RELEASE strings in lua.h
   (svn r20367)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
